summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Fifteenth Avenue Northeast, from East 40th Street to Brintual Place, et al, in the City of Seattle, by grading under Ordinance No. 18662, creating Local Improvement District No. 1763 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
